><\/blockquote><p style=\"text-align: right;\">Forough Farrokhzad,<\/p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u00a0<em>Let Us Believe in The Beginning of The Cold Season<\/em><\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>The era we live in constantly challenges our visual perception and memory, as it is bombarded with images and information, along with an ever-shifting phase in our daily lives and spaces we experience. We rarely \u2018look\u2019 at anything or pay enough attention to them, while these floating moments, particles with which we build our minds and memories, offer us unique mental spaces to reflect on life and its details. Like Forough\u2019s beautiful poem, even the simplest act of \u2018passing by a wet tree\u2019 has a weight we take for granted and overlook.<\/p><p>I see this website as a platform where I can delve into this space and reflect on subjects that encompass life, environment, and their representation in visual arts and cinema. Whether it is just archiving documentary urban photos or digital collages, or writing down about films, \u201cFrames and Distances\u201d strives to overcome this distance between our minds, our perceptions, and the subjects presented within a frame.<\/p><p>Hopefully, this time, I&#8217;ll be aware that I\u2019m passing by the wet trees.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6ae75cd elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"6ae75cd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/framesanddistances.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/Nastaran-Bagheri-Portfolio.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Portfolio<\/span>\n\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\